'''Boria Majumdar''' is an Indian sports journalist, academician and author.

Majumdar was born on 8 March 1976 at [[Kolkata]]. He completed his schooling from [[The Frank Anthony Public School, Kolkata]]. He completed BA & MA in history from [[University of Calcutta]]. He was awarded [[Doctor of Philosophy|DPhil]] in History from [[University of Oxford]] in 2004 where he was [[Rhodes Scholarship|Rhodes scholar]].<ref name=\:0\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.uclan.ac.uk/staff_profiles/professor_boria_majumdar.php|title=Professor Boria Majumdar {{!}} Staff Profile {{!}}University of Central Lancashire|website=UCLan - University of Central Lancashire|language=en|access-date=2019-01-11}}</ref><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldwhoswho.com/public/views/entry.html?id=sl2170547|title=Majumdar Boria : World Who's Who|website=www.worldwhoswho.com|access-date=2019-01-11}}</ref>

